            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "As a CJK user, I think it would be nice if Neovim could support IM auto-switching on all platforms. However maybe it is not that easy (or even possible) to make the feature work out of the box on all environments.\r\n\r\nIn addition to ordinary usage, when TUI Neovim is used through ssh on another machine, the IM on local machine should be switched instead, which makes the problem even more complicated.",
